select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc 
STOCKS_LIST.txt

正在處理 0060
('0060',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc 
No data found!!!

正在處理 1201
('1201',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc 
正在處理 1203
('1203',)

正在處理 1227
('1227',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1259
('1259',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1305
('1305',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1321
('1321',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1341
('1341',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1419
('1419',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1442
('1442',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1455
('1455',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1469
('1469',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1506
('1506',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1524
('1524',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1536
('1536',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1568
('1568',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1590
('1590',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1604
('1604',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1618
('1618',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1713
('1713',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1726
('1726',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1742
('1742',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1785
('1785',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1808
('1808',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 1907
('1907',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

('2015',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc 
正在處理 2017
('2017',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2031
('2031',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2064
('2064',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2103
('2103',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2206
('2206',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2236
('2236',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2252
('2252',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2313
('2313',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2330
('2330',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2349
('2349',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

('2361',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2375
('2375',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2392
('2392',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

('2407',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2423
('2423',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

('2436',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2450
('2450',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2462
('2462',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2477
('2477',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2491
('2491',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2506
('2506',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2534
('2534',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2547
('2547',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2609
('2609',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2633
('2633',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2704
('2704',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2727
('2727',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2743
('2743',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2801
('2801',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2841
('2841',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2881
('2881',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2892
('2892',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2913
('2913',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 2939
('2939',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3008
('3008',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3022
('3022',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3033
('3033',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3045
('3045',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3057
('3057',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3078
('3078',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3095
('3095',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3135
('3135',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3164
('3164',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3202
('3202',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3224
('3224',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3257
('3257',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3287
('3287',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3305
('3305',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3323
('3323',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3360
('3360',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3390
('3390',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc
