正在處理 3434
('3434',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3465
('3465',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3492
('3492',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3516
('3516',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3530
('3530',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3546
('3546',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3561
('3561',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3581
('3581',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3597
('3597',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3624
('3624',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3646
('3646',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3669
('3669',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3687
('3687',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 3706
('3706',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4104
('4104',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4119
('4119',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4133
('4133',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4151
('4151',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4166
('4166',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4186
('4186',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4304
('4304',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4419
('4419',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4441
('4441',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4530
('4530',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4543
('4543',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4556
('4556',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4568
('4568',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4583
('4583',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4720
('4720',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4737
('4737',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4755
('4755',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4803
('4803',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4911
('4911',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4933
('4933',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4950
('4950',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4968
('4968',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 4989
('4989',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc 
正在處理 4991
('4991',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5016
('5016',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5213
('5213',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5236
('5236',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5262
('5262',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5278
('5278',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5299
('5299',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5317
('5317',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5351
('5351',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5388
('5388',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5439
('5439',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5469
('5469',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5489
('5489',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5515
('5515',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5533
('5533',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5608
('5608',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 5876
('5876',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6016
('6016',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6104
('6104',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6117
('6117',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6129
('6129',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6142
('6142',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6154
('6154',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6168
('6168',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6180
('6180',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6192
('6192',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6205
('6205',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6216
('6216',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6227
('6227',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6239
('6239',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6251
('6251',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6272
('6272',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6285
('6285',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6404
('6404',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6419
('6419',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6441
('6441',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6464
('6464',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6486
('6486',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6504
('6504',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6518
('6518',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc
