正在處理 6538
('6538',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6552
('6552',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6566
('6566',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6579
('6579',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6591
('6591',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6606
('6606',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6621
('6621',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6641
('6641',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6657
('6657',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6671
('6671',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6689
('6689',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6703
('6703',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6721
('6721',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6735
('6735',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6750
('6750',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6763
('6763',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6784
('6784',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6796
('6796',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6813
('6813',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6826
('6826',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6839
('6839',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6857
('6857',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 6875
('6875',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 7530
('7530',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8011
('8011',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8040
('8040',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8053
('8053',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8074
('8074',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8087
('8087',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8104
('8104',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8131
('8131',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8210
('8210',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8271
('8271',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8341
('8341',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8403
('8403',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8422
('8422',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8437
('8437',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8462
('8462',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8480
('8480',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8905
('8905',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8927
('8927',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 8938
('8938',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

('9188',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 9914
('9914',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 9930
('9930',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

正在處理 9943
('9943',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc

('9962',)
select a.股票代號, d.stock_name as 股票名稱, a.年度, a.累計營收_億, a.累計營收年增_百分比, b.股本_億, b.財報評分, b.年度股價_收盤, b.年度股價_平均, b.roe, b.roa, b.bps, c.股利所屬期間, c.股利合計, c.年均殖利率_合計, c.eps, c.盈餘分配率_合計 from ( select stock_no as 股票代號, mid(cast(date as char),1,4) as 年度, cum_revenue as 累計營收_億, ann_ins_cum_revenue_p as 累計營收年增_百分比 from stocks_sale_month where mid(cast(date as char),5,2) = '12' ) a left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, year as 年度, share_capital as 股本_億, fin_report_score as 財報評分, ann_stock_end_price as 年度股價_收盤, ann_stock_avg_price as 年度股價_平均, roe, roa, bps from STOCKS_BZ_PERFORMANCE ) b on a.股票代號 = b.股票代號 and a.年度 = b.年度 left outer join ( select stock_no as 股票代號, period_of_dividend as 股利所屬期間, total_dividend as 股利合計, year_high_price as 年度股價最高價, year_low_price as 年度股價最低價, year_avg_price as 年度股價年均價, avg_ann_yield as 年均殖利率_合計, eps, earnings_dis_ratio as 盈餘分配率_合計 from STOCKS_DIVIDEND ) c on a.股票代號 = c.股票代號 and a.年度 = c.股利所屬期間 left outer join stocks_name d on a.股票代號 = d.stock_no where a.股票代號 = %s order by a.年度 desc 
資料處理完成!! 共 2178 筆。
